---
title: Pesto Halloumi Bun with Basil Aioli and Potato Wedges
description: This simple veggie burger is jam-packed with comforting halloumi cheese, creamy basil aioli, bright tomatoes and fresh spring mix! Served with roasted potato wedges, dinner never seemed so easy!
